column5: Well back............... Great time...........   Kids had a very good time and are still wore out.  Bad news is............... No fishing  Even stayed a extra night to get to the rest of the attractions..........   A week just isnt enough time.  Maybe next time
Get some rest Bubba, but try not to sleep on yer face,eh!
You'll find time a plenty fer fishin' amigo. The kids will be thankin you dearly, fer such a good time!
Should have walked down to the Maid of the Mist docks..  There are some huge smallmouths roaming around there
